name: Timeline
heading: Some of the achievements and employments I had

timeline.title: Started Job at Twzeef
timeline.content: I started my first full-time job at Twzeef as a Full stack developer with react as front-end and nodejs express as back-end

timeline.title: ICCCEEE19 publication
timeline.content: A publication that I made in ICCCEEE19 (International Conference on Computer, Control, Electrical and Electronics Engineering) of the name 'Build and conquer: Solving N queens problem with iterative compression'

timeline.title: ICCCEEE19 Best Paper in AI Track
timeline.content: The publication of the name 'Build and conquer: Solving N queens problem with iterative compression' won the best paper at the AI track in ICCCEEE19 (International Conference on Computer, Control, Electrical and Electronics Engineering)

timeline.title: ICCCEEE20 publication
timeline.content: A publication that I made in ICCCEEE20 (International Conference on Computer, Control, Electrical and Electronics Engineering) of the name 'Adjusting Street Plans Using Deep Reinforcement Learning'

timeline.title: Started Job at Exit:funds
timeline.content: I started my part-time job at Exit:funds as a Full stack mobile developer with flutter in application UI and firebase as back-end

timeline.title: Started Job at Engima AI
timeline.content: I started my full-time job at Engima AI as a Full stack developer with react as front-end and nodejs express as back-end
